Class EmbulkSystemProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Dictionary<K,V>

          • org.embulk.EmbulkSystemProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<java.lang.Object,java.lang.Object>

    public final class EmbulkSystemProperties
extends java.util.Properties
    Embulk's system config as Properties that do not permit any modification once created.

    Plugins MUST NOT use this class. No any compatibility is guaranteed.
